predictions.question: How many singers do we have?
What are the names of singers who have a concert in 2014?
predictions.predicted_sql: SELECT T1.name FROM singer AS T1 JOIN singer_in_concert AS T2 ON T1.singer_id = T2.singer_id JOIN concert AS T3 ON T2.concert_id = T3.concert_id WHERE T3.year = 2014
